Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.08,0:01:06.58,OP2_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(644,24)\fad(100,100)\blur2}将心冰冻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:13.34,OP2_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(644,24)\fad(100,100)\blur2}小小的双手却无法承担起的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:20.18,OP2_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(644,24)\fad(100,100)\blur2}梦想终会超越现实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.30,0:01:28.10,OP2_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(644,24)\fad(100,500)\blur2}尽管一直深埋于虚幻的海中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:31.15,OP2_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(644,24)\fad(100,100)\blur2}想立刻传达于你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.19,0:01:35.15,OP2_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(644,24)\fad(100,100)\blur2}穿过哀伤的天际
