Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.23,0:00:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者大人回到原来世界的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.31,0:00:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在过于悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为大家全力以赴的勇者大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.19,0:00:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连一起生活过的记忆都不能带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样真是太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲伤的离别
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.24,0:00:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是最讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.98,0:02:01.44,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1020)\fs52\blur4\3c&H3B5D92&\fsp2\pos(252,710)}「约定」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也吃不下了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假大概是在多少天之后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.18,0:02:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…如果以地球时间来说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.05,0:02:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是4月4号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.93,0:02:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有100多天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.89,0:02:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,100天么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.02,0:02:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么长时间见不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.73,0:02:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会很寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.40,0:02:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 如果只是两三天的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.61,0:02:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以利用连续休假的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.98,0:02:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有紧急情况的话请随时叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 谢谢你 真红
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.53,0:02:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:02:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的典礼必须要办么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.95,0:03:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 因为真红是勇者大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢送典礼必须要好好举办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.80,0:03:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比斯科帝的勇者真红
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.76,0:03:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了召唤的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.22,0:03:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将于今日回到故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把勇者之剑 神剑帕拉迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.18,0:03:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交还给召唤者 米露茜欧莱公主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.88,0:03:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.55,0:03:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多等下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用和勇者大人悲伤离别的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.72,0:03:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻过这一页的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找下一份资料的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许就能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.19,0:04:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 再等下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉歌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 真的对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.75,0:04:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉歌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然是个没用的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉歌 为了我这么努力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能没法把记忆啊什么的带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 即使这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也绝不忘记 一定会想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.57,0:04:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:04:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有礼物给莉歌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:04:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.83,0:04:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四色圆珠笔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有便携音箱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然手机不能给你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有这些的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以拆开玩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会…拆开的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.42,0:05:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好保管的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远 永远
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 莉歌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 到最后都要麻烦我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾克蕾来给我送行我很高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下已经在召唤台准备召还
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不能慢慢悠悠的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有件事 艾克蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.51,0:05:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 虽然是件老物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.76,0:05:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的话能收下这个么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.14,0:06:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 先放我这吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 好像也给别人礼物了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达尔琪安卿和骑士团长的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.82,0:06:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给了钱包里的纪念硬币每人一枚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手机链给了尤吉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.99,0:06:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.74,0:06:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像分赠遗物一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人扫兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.91,0:06:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然被召还回去的话就没法回到弗洛尼亚鲁多了么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.59,0:06:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像会失去记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里度过的每天的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.31,0:06:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候发现的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.98,0:06:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要看到莉歌的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.90,0:06:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.69,0:06:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 听说来的时候很简单的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到回去时会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.74,0:07:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是荒唐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.87,0:07:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 不过我不会忘记的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在弗洛尼亚鲁多经历的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家相遇的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和身材娇小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.29,0:07:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但又坚强而直率的亲卫队长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.17,0:07:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾克蕾尔一起经历的种种
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.26,0:07:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没有自信能记得你这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是训练 战争 还是外交
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每天都很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我真寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被忘记会寂寞的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不想被忘记的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.70,0:07:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论发生什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.91,0:07:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也别把我们忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后给我尽快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.13,0:07:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 旋风
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.95,0:08:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.87,0:08:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他说想送你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.33,0:08:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召还的时候只有我和真红才能在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旋风 趁现在和真红道别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 也谢谢你了 旋风
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.48,0:08:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待期间将会准备仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间一到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与来时相反
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.61,0:09:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红将会从这里飞上天空
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能回到原来的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然来这边没有多长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却总觉得已经过去很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里和真红相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红成为勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.56,0:09:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经历了许多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 最重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.77,0:09:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红到来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与真红一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.02,0:09:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常的 非常的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.62,0:09:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.95,0:09:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被召唤到比斯科帝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.33,0:09:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:09:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.71,0:10:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次暑假的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.59,0:10:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.30,0:10:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次肯定会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加 更加…愉快的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.77,0:10:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红 不可以哭的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.35,0:10:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定 一定会再见面的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们肯定会记得你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.15,0:10:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会把我们忘记的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.12,0:10:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会忘记的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.45,0:10:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对 绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.89,0:10:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了… 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.28,0:11:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红 真红！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.71,0:11:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别回去 我不让你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.38,0:11:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还要一直 一直 一直
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.34,0:11:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和真红在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的事 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.68,0:11:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.68,0:11:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和公主殿下 和大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.35,0:11:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.52,0:11:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.48,0:11:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 米露茜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直一直都最喜欢真红了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.32,0:11:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.99,0:11:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:11:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.66,0:12:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我一定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.46,0:12:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会来见你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会遵守诺言的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.54,0:12:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红 起来了么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.21,0:12:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.17,0:12:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:12:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.26,0:12:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓琪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 不是起来了么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.39,0:13:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹应我一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 刚刚起来么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.16,0:13:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么是这么回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春假刚开始的两周
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然觉得自己去了什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.71,0:13:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却不记得自己去了哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.55,0:13:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过总觉得很难过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记忆丧失 撞到头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 84000条结果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用搜索什么的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.86,0:13:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.40,0:13:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得不是撞到头了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.07,0:13:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:13:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太想得起来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.45,0:14:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.83,0:14:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 还是先去下医院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉还是让医生看下比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 没事 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.50,0:14:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅游的事也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要联系下叔叔阿姨么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 蓓琪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 真的没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了早饭 就出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得是很开心的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.52,0:14:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 是急性健忘症么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能会因为某种契机突然想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.59,0:14:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.29,0:14:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不过是个平凡的中学一年级学生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为好朋友 温柔的蓓琪一直守候在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.67,0:14:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春假结束的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.34,0:14:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是二年级学生了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红 蓓琪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有既是亲戚又是师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.68,0:15:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是对手的七海
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.44,0:15:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人果然都好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见的问候就突然这样么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七海 好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红 来亲一亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.91,0:15:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七海真是一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有作为海洋学者的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海样生物学者的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.13,0:15:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些事情完全没忘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.35,0:15:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉像是忘记了很重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.57,0:16:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是突然丢掉了珍贵的宝物一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀揣不安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.23,0:16:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.67,0:16:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 吵醒你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.14,0:16:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到真红的归乡这么辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早点发现就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.85,0:16:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那是勇者大人的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是从加雷特图书馆拿过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于召唤的书籍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.49,0:16:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.16,0:16:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个蜡印
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是比斯科帝领主的东西么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.04,0:16:56.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,0)\pos(640,570)}致王立研究院 关于勇者召唤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将召唤而来的勇者逆召唤的注意事项
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆召唤是在勇者拒绝和召唤者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.39,0:17:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及弗洛尼亚鲁多有所牵扯时的唯一办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.94,0:17:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者不能从弗洛尼亚鲁多带走包括记忆在内的所有东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这段记忆不会立即消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.83,0:17:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从召还后开始 处于记忆封锁的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到记忆全部消失 需要花上半年多的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.38,0:17:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 如果把逆召唤的勇者再召唤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.72,0:17:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要满足以下条件
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其一 逆召唤和再召唤必须相差90日以上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.56,0:18:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其二 除了召唤者之外 必须要有3名以上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.28,0:18:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到作为勇者会再次到访弗洛尼亚鲁多的信物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即勇者的随身物品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.41,0:18:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然物品没有限制 但最好是勇者从原来的世界带来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.05,0:18:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其三
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.97,0:18:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大清早真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.93,0:18:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 勇者大人放什么东西在你这了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 典礼之后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.19,0:18:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红说他回去之后再让我打开 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.78,0:18:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 还没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.95,0:18:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让您打开看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定 说不定会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.29,0:18:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于召唤者 勇者须交给其契约之书和约定信物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契约之书除了记录回归的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.36,0:19:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还必须签上勇者和召唤者的姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.68,0:19:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致我深爱的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.60,0:19:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米露茜欧莱{\fnsimhei}·{\r}F{\fnsimhei}·{\r}比斯科帝殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.65,0:19:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者真红和泉向您传达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.15,0:19:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感激 爱和友情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.48,0:19:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再启 我一定会再回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.57,0:19:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是作为勇者的承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.08,0:19:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 这样就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.54,0:19:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对勇者大人的再召唤就可以实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.63,0:19:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.17,0:19:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者大人果然好好的遵守了约定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.27,0:20:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.06,0:20:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.40,0:20:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓琪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.31,0:20:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓琪 蓓琪 蓓琪 蓓琪 蓓琪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.61,0:20:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 真红
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.20,0:20:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓琪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.34,0:20:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}啊 真红…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.24,0:20:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.67,0:21:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.08,0:21:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.75,0:21:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.21,0:21:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超开心的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了许多愉快的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.05,0:21:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也交到了很多好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.82,0:21:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假的时候 蓓琪也和我一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.85,0:21:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.64,0:21:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 可以去的话我就去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.68,0:21:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红 蓓琪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.10,0:21:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人玩太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.98,0:21:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.61,0:21:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.56,0:21:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 等…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.37,0:21:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中学一年级到二年级的春假
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.79,0:21:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.26,0:21:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假也还会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.29,0:21:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到那里成为勇者！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
